**XAI Easy** is a powerful Python package designed to make machine learning models interpretable and explainable. Whether you're working with classification, regression, or clustering models, XAI Easy provides comprehensive tools to understand what your models are doing and why they make specific predictions.

### Key Features
- ğŸ¯ **Global Model Explanations** - Understand feature importance across your entire dataset
- ğŸ” **Local Instance Explanations** - Explain individual predictions with precision
- ğŸ“Š **Professional Visualizations** - Generate publication-ready charts and interactive reports
- ğŸ¨ **Modern HTML Reports** - Create stunning, responsive reports with professional branding
- âš¡ **Model Agnostic** - Works with any scikit-learn compatible model
- ğŸ”§ **SHAP Integration** - Automatic integration with SHAP when available

